description: A team of non-human naval officers, explorers, conservationists, filmmakers, innovators, and scientists, have discovered at a depth of up to 999 xtz under the Adriatic Sea a VHS tape with unpublished images of a Baby Supernova from 1972. An original artwork by Iskra Velitchkova.
